queryText:
with tmp0 as (
select
    a.ds,
    a.prod_id as sku_code,
    a.sap_store_code,
    a.stock_prod_qty_1d_ste,
    a.stock_prod_qty_1d_stb,
    0 as sale_qty
from ads.ads_scm_store_jxcrpt_1d a
left join dim.dim_store_info_lastest t1 on a.sap_store_code=t1.sap_store_code
where a.ds > date_sub('2021-05-08',28) and  a.ds <= '2021-05-08' and t1.sts_state = '3A'
union all
select
        a.ds,
        a.sku_code,
        a.sap_store_code ,
        0 as stock_prod_qty_1d_ste ,
        0 as stock_prod_qty_1d_stb ,
        a.sale_qty
    from dwd.dws_rpt_store_goods_sale_query_df a
    left join dim.dim_store_info_lastest t1 on a.sap_store_code=t1.sap_store_code
    where a.ds > date_sub('2021-05-08',28) and  a.ds <= '2021-05-08' and t1.sts_state = '3A'
)
,
tmp as(
    select
           a.sku_code,
           a.sap_store_code,
           count(case when stock_prod_qty_1d_ste > 0 and stock_prod_qty_1d_stb > 0 and ds > date_sub('2021-05-08',7) then a.sap_store_code end ) as store_day_7,     --近7天符合条件门店数 --日均销门店数
           count(case when stock_prod_qty_1d_ste > 0 and stock_prod_qty_1d_stb > 0 and ds > date_sub('2021-05-08',28) then a.sap_store_code end) as store_day_28,    --近28天符合条件门店数 --日均销门店数
           sum(case when stock_prod_qty_1d_ste > 0 and stock_prod_qty_1d_stb > 0 and ds > date_sub('2021-05-08',7) then a.sale_qty else 0 end) as sale_qty_7,  --近七天符合条件销售数量  --日均销销量
           sum(case when stock_prod_qty_1d_ste > 0 and stock_prod_qty_1d_stb > 0 and ds > date_sub('2021-05-08',28) then a.sale_qty else 0 end) as sale_qty_28  --近28天符合条件销售数量  --日均销销量
    from (
        select
               ds,
               sku_code,
               sap_store_code,
               sum(stock_prod_qty_1d_ste) as stock_prod_qty_1d_ste,
               sum(stock_prod_qty_1d_stb) as stock_prod_qty_1d_stb,
               sum(sale_qty) as sale_qty
        from tmp0
        group by ds,sku_code,sap_store_code
    )a
    group by a.sku_code,a.sap_store_code
)
,store_area as (
select
       a.sap_store_code,
case when a.area_class1_name = '西藏区' then '西藏区' else b.area end as area
from dim.dim_store_lastest  a
left join ods.ods_youdata_442_miniso_sccm_sales_area b on a.comm_opt_manager = b.manager
where a.area_class1_name in ('西藏区','华东经营大区','华北经营大区','华西经营大区','华南经营大区','华中经营大区')
)

insert overwrite table ads.ads_ds_miniso_sccm_delivery_goods_store_detail partition(ds)
select
    a.stat_date                -- '统计日期'
   ,a.wrh_code                 -- '仓库代码'
   ,a.wrh_name                 -- '仓库名称'
   ,'C1' as cate1_code         --'大类2代码'
   ,t.cate1_name               -- '大类2名称'
   ,t.cate_code                -- '细类代码'
   ,t.cate_name                -- '细类名称'
   ,a.sku_code                 -- '商品代码'
   ,t.sku_name                --'商品名称'
   ,t.pkg_price                -- '组合价'
   ,a.store_code               -- '门店代码'
   ,a.store_name               -- '门店名称'
   ,d.area  --运营区域

   ,(c.sale_qty_7/c.store_day_7)  as avg_sales_qty_7days      -- '单店日均销量（7天）'
   ,(c.sale_qty_28/c.store_day_28)  as avg_sales_qty_28days     -- '单店日均销量（28天）'

   ,b.hav_stock_store_qty      -- '当前有库存门店数'
   ,b.hav_sales_rate_7days     -- '7天动销率'
   ,b.being_wrh_turnover_days   -- '即将入仓周转'
   ,b.wrh_turnover_days        -- '仓库周转'
   ,a.zh_days                  -- '门店周转'

   ,c.sale_qty_7 as sales_qty_7days          -- '销售量-7天（总）'
   ,c.sale_qty_28 as sales_qty_28days         -- '销售量-28天（总）'
   ,date_format(current_timestamp(), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss')
   ,a.ds
from ads.tmp_05_ads_ds_miniso_sccm_goods_wrh_detail_mid a
left join ads.ads_ds_miniso_sccm_goods_wrh_detail_mid b on a.wrh_code = b.wrh_code and a.sku_code = b.sku_code and b.ds ='2021-05-08'
left join tmp c on a.sku_code = c.sku_code and a.store_code = c.sap_store_code
left join store_area d on a.store_code = d.sap_store_code
left join ads.tmp_01_ads_ds_miniso_sccm_goods_detail_mid t on a.sku_code = t.sku_code and t.ds ='2021-05-08'
where a.ds ='2021-05-08'
